      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1775305469,
      "updated": 1775305472
    },
    {
      "id": "69d102ff000000000021c095",
      "text": "[https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8bh9uY_ZaKY]",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1775305472,
      "updated": 1775305472
    },
    {
      "id": "69d10300000000000021c097",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1775305472,
      "updated": 1775305472
    },
    {
      "id": "69d10304000000000021c099",
      "text": "パターンを用いた内言/会話のやり取りがCosenseっぽい",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1775305476,
      "updated": 1775305492
    },
    {
      "id": "69d10366000000000021c09d",
      "text": " 例えば1:36だと",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1775305575,
      "updated": 1775305582
    },
    {
      "id": "69d10301000000000021c098",
      "text": "  > なるほど！このチームは[共感のチームづくり]ができているんだな！",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1775305473,
      "updated": 1775305582
    },
    {
      "id": "69d10351000000000021c09c",
      "text": "  \t> あ！[ゴールへの道のり]が不明確だからうまくいってないんだ！",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1775305554,
      "updated": 1775305717
    },
    {
      "id": "69d10300000000000021c096",
      "text": " ページ名(概念の名前)を引用しながら話すところがCosenseっぽい",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1775305472,
      "updated": 1775305609
    },
    {
      "id": "69d10388000000000021c09f",
      "text": " Cosenseだと、↓他人が見つけた概念をページ名で引用しながら話す",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1775305609,
      "updated": 1775305700
    },
    {
      "id": "69d1038c000000000021c0a0",
      "text": "  from [2026/04/04#69d07c7a0000000000ef452c]",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1775305612,
      "updated": 1775305670
    },
    {
      "id": "69d10372000000000021c09e",
      "text": "   >専門学校で授業を受けてたときに、教科書に入る前にプリントが配布されて計算を練習した",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1775305586,
      "updated": 1775305706
    },
    {
      "id": "69d103cf000000000021c0a2",
      "text": "   >  中学校や高校でやった内容をやり直すもの",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1775305679,
      "updated": 1775305706
    },
    {
      "id": "69d103cf000000000021c0a3",
      "text": "   >  [ちょっと違う話だ。言いたいだけだった]になってきた",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1775305679,
      "updated": 1775305706
    },
